reviewText: arrived on time and in good condition.  This is a Bulldog Drummond story with Tom Conway in the lead. I like Conway especially as the Falcon. Here he is good but the story is not as good as a Falcon story.  Still I enjoyed the movie.

I like Bulldog Drummd and didn't realize there were other movies that around other than what I already owned.  I enjoy Tom Conway very much so this was another great movie, glad I discovered it and bought it.
